assive increase in solar capacity (ie installs.) Simply put, &#8220;the mor=
e solar panels we</span><sup> </sup><span>produce, the cheaper they get.&#8=
221;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-he=
ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The question is: can we keep it up or have=
